WEBVTT

00:00:00.830 --> 00:00:05.334
I come from one of the most
beautiful places in the world,

00:00:05.376 --> 00:00:06.711
Papua New Guinea.

00:00:06.753 --> 00:00:09.881
Papua New Guinea is wonderful
for many reasons.

00:00:09.922 --> 00:00:13.801
Our lush vegetation, our seas,

00:00:13.843 --> 00:00:16.679
islands, lakes and forests.

00:00:17.180 --> 00:00:21.309
Also, our unique and remarkable
cultural diversity.

00:00:21.934 --> 00:00:24.395
Not to forget our people.

00:00:25.063 --> 00:00:27.648
And also, not to mention our climate.

00:00:27.648 --> 00:00:31.444
It's basically 27 degrees Celsius,